  "title": "n8n API: Test API authentication",
  "body": "curl -v -X GET \"{{n8n-url}}/api/v1/workflows\" \\\n  -H \"X-N8N-API-KEY: {{api-key}}\" \\\n  -H \"Accept: application/json\" 2>&1 | grep -E '(HTTP/|X-N8N)'",
  "description": "Test API key authentication with verbose output - verify API access (docs.n8n.io/api/authentication/)",
